articles.description: It wasn't just Caitlin Clark who made history for the Indiana Fever on Friday against the Las Vegas Aces.
articles.content:
Caitlin Clark stole the show on Friday, September 13. This is after the Indiana Fever rookie sensation set a new WNBA record for the most assists in a single season.
